  ('optometrist-moex-00588', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-112-b0a2f330', 'sub-optometrist-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關視網膜的構造與生理，下列何者錯誤？', '["外界膜（externallimitingmembrane）介於視網膜及玻璃體間", "內網狀層（innerplexiformlayer）包含雙極細胞（bipolarcells）、無軸突細胞（amacrinecells）的軸突（axon）", "內核層（innernuclearlayer）由水平細胞（horizontalcells）、雙極細胞（bipolarcells）及無軸突細胞（amacrine cells）所構成", "外核層（outernuclearlayer）為感光細胞之細胞核（thenucleiofthephotoreceptors）組成"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:42+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "47389aa2fc18", "answer_pdf_sha1": "723eb96326a4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "109", "s": "0901", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼球解剖生理學與倫理法規", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 29, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00589', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-112-b0a2f330', 'sub-optometrist-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '王先生兩眼同時平行往左轉，此時有那些神經在控制這種動作？①第三對腦神經  ②第四對腦神經  ③第', '["第六對腦神經", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:42+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "47389aa2fc18", "answer_pdf_sha1": "723eb96326a4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "109", "s": "0901", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼球解剖生理學與倫理法規", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 30, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00590', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-112-b0a2f330', 'sub-optometrist-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於第三對腦神經，下列敘述何者正確？', '["神經核位於中腦（midbrain）的下丘（inferiorcolliculus）", "通常受傷、動脈瘤（aneurysm）等外科疾病所造成的第三對腦神經損傷，不太會影響瞳孔（pupil）的反應", "第三對腦神經受傷的病患眼睛會無法緊閉", "發生單一第三對腦神經麻痺的病灶，通常位於神經的基底部（basilarportion）"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:42+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "47389aa2fc18", "answer_pdf_sha1": "723eb96326a4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "109", "s": "0901", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼球解剖生理學與倫理法規", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 31, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00591', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-112-b0a2f330', 'sub-optometrist-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關眼外肌發育的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["控制眼球運動的眼外肌共有6條，由間質層（mesenchyme）的同一塊組織分化而成", "下斜肌（inferiorobliquemuscle）由第三對腦神經支配運動", "提瞼肌（levatorpalpebraesuperioris）與上斜肌（superiorobliquemuscle）同源，所以眼瞼下垂的病人常 會合併上斜肌麻痺", "外直肌（lateralrectusmuscle）由第六對腦神經支配運動"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:42+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "47389aa2fc18", "answer_pdf_sha1": "723eb96326a4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "109", "s": "0901", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼球解剖生理學與倫理法規", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 32, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
